                    </div>
                    <span>Unlike "A reader", I think this book is valuable. It is indeed a hodge podge collection of contributions from many authors and their styles are certainly different. But that is OK. This is not a novel, it is a toolkit, and an excellent one. Take what you need when you need it and leave the rest alone.
<br /> </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Fantastic value</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
