                    <span>This is a great book.  It has contributions from 45 different authors.  The contributions are too many to list but include such areas as 360 surveys, coaching, managing change, teambuilding and many more.  You are also able to download many of these which allows for easy duplication.  For the price it is a tremendous value.  I am glad that I purchased it.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent, excellent, excellent!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
